#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.map.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.map"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map:1 of
msgid "Map values of Series according to input correspondence."
msgstr "根据输入的对应关系映射 Series 的值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map:3 of
msgid ""
"Used for substituting each value in a Series with another value, that may"
" be derived from a function, a ``dict`` or a :class:`Series`."
msgstr ""
"用于将 Series 中的每个值替换为另一个值，该值可能来源于函数、``dict`` 或 :"
"class:`Series`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map:7 of
msgid "Mapping correspondence."
msgstr "映射对应关系。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map:9 of
msgid ""
"If 'ignore', propagate NaN values, without passing them to the mapping "
"correspondence."
msgstr "如果为 'ignore'，则传播 NaN 值，而不将其传递给映射对应关系。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map:12 of
msgid ""
"Specify return type of the function. Must be specified when we cannot "
"decide the return type of the function."
msgstr "指定函数的返回类型。当无法确定函数的返回类型时必须指定。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map:15 of
msgid "Specify the scale of memory uses in the function versus input size."
msgstr "指定函数中内存使用量相对于输入大小的规模。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map:18 of
msgid "Whether infer dtypes when dtypes or output_type is not specified"
msgstr "当未指定 dtypes 或 output_type 时是否推断数据类型"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map:21 of
msgid "Same index as caller."
msgstr "与调用者相同的索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map:26 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.apply`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map:27 of
msgid "For applying more complex functions on a Series."
msgstr "用于在 Series 上应用更复杂的函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.apply`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map:30 of
msgid "Apply a function row-/column-wise."
msgstr "按行或列应用函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map:32 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.applymap`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map:33 of
msgid "Apply a function elementwise on a whole DataFrame."
msgstr "在整个 DataFrame 上逐元素应用函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map:36 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map:37 of
msgid ""
"When ``arg`` is a dictionary, values in Series that are not in the "
"dictionary (as keys) are converted to ``NaN``. However, if the dictionary"
" is a ``dict`` subclass that defines ``__missing__`` (i.e. provides a "
"method for default values), then this default is used rather than "
"``NaN``."
msgstr ""
"当 ``arg`` 是字典时，Series 中不在字典中的值（作为键）将被转换为 ``NaN``"
"。但如果该字典是定义了 ``__missing__`` 的 ``dict`` 子类（即提供了默认值的"
"方法），则使用该默认值而不是 ``NaN``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map:44 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map:55 of
msgid ""
"``map`` accepts a ``dict`` or a ``Series``. Values that are not found in "
"the ``dict`` are converted to ``NaN``, unless the dict has a default "
"value (e.g. ``defaultdict``):"
msgstr ""
"``map`` 接受 ``dict`` 或 ``Series``。在 ``dict`` 中找不到的值将被转换为 `"
"`NaN``，除非该字典具有默认值（例如 ``defaultdict``）："

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map:66 of
msgid "It also accepts a function:"
msgstr "它也接受一个函数："

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.map.series_map:75 of
msgid ""
"To avoid applying the function to missing values (and keep them as "
"``NaN``) ``na_action='ignore'`` can be used:"
msgstr ""
"为了避免将函数应用于缺失值（并保持它们为 ``NaN``），可以使用 ``na_action="
"'ignore'``："

